test_positive_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4] == []
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 2, 3, 4]
test_even_range:
assert [-2, -4] == [-2, -4, -6, -8, -10]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: -6
  Full diff:
  - [-2, -4, -6, -8, -10]
  + [-2, -4]
test_large_range:
assert [0, 1, 2, 3, 4] == []
  Left contains 5 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0, 1, 2, 3, 4]
